  "prompt": "Which companies work for advertising and promotion of FlipKart?",
  "response": "Flipkart collaborates with various advertising and promotion agencies to enhance its brand visibility and market its products effectively. Some of the noteworthy companies that have worked with Flipkart in the past include:\n\n1. **Ogilvy & Mather** - A renowned global advertising and public relations agency that has provided creative services to Flipkart.\n2. **Dentsu Aegis Network** - This global media and digital marketing communications company has worked on Flipkart's digital campaigns and media buying.\n3. **GroupM** - A leading media investment company, part of WPP, which has supported Flipkart with media planning and buying.\n4. **Publicis Groupe** - Specifically, agencies under this group like Leo Burnett have been involved in creating advertising content for Flipkart.\n5. **WATConsult** - A consulting firm specializing in social media and digital marketing strategies, which has handled some of Flipkart's social media promotions.\n6. **Performics** - Part of the Publicis Groupe, this performance marketing agency has assisted in digital marketing and search engine optimization efforts for Flipkart.\n7. **Mindshare** - Another WPP entity that has been instrumental in strategizing and executing media campaigns for Flipkart.\n8. **BBH India** - Bartle Bogle Hegarty (BBH) has provided creative advertising solutions for Flipkart in terms of branding and television commercials.\n9. **SapientRazorfish** - Part of Publicis Groupe, this digital transformation agency has worked on enhancing Flipkart\u2019s digital presence and e-commerce strategies.\n\nThese agencies have helped Flipkart build its brand, target the right audience, and optimize its marketing efforts across various platforms.",
